{"tid":1895943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白金漢宮遞奪頭銜阻止哈利夫婦用至室名義賺錢 哈利夫婦指女皇及政府都無權阻止他們海外用王室這詞","createTime":"2020-02-24T23:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:22:11.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"57885830a3eae9c98649095821fb082cf0139039","tid":1895943,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:35:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3077789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3077789&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=55cc7bf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3077789&h=76405dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3077789</a><br />\n<br />\n英國哈利王子與妻子梅根將在3月底，正式卸下王室職務，白金漢宮1月時發布聲明，兩人將不再使用王室「殿下（HRH）」頭銜，更指出哈利夫婦的商標不能再保有「王室」（Royal）一詞，對此哈利夫婦日前發布聲明表示，君主或是內閣辦公室都無權禁止兩人在海外使用「王室」一詞。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，英國哈利王子與妻子梅根在當地時間週五晚間於官方網站發布聲明，宣布未來將不會在任何地區使用「薩塞克斯王室」（Sussex Royal）一稱。數小時後兩人再次發布聲明指出，女王對「王室」一詞沒有實質管轄權，若兩人堅持在海外使用「王室」，女王或是英國政府都無法阻止。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，哈利夫婦對於不能同時擁有王室身分和外部工作感到遺憾，並暗指白金漢宮對兩人有不公平待遇，聲明中提到，「儘管已有其他具頭銜的成員在王室外求職的先例，薩塞克斯公爵夫婦則將接受12個月的審查期」。<br />\n<br />\n哈利夫婦在去年底以「薩塞克斯王室」向英國智慧財產局（Intellectual Property Office）註冊超過上百品項商標權，包括服飾、印刷、社福等領域，兩人的基金會、官方網站、Instagram也使用了這個名稱。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，哈利和梅根兩人未來將持續發展非營利組織，由於英國政府對「王室」一詞的具體規定，兩人將不再使用「薩塞克斯王室」這個名稱，或以任何形式使用「王室」一詞，目前也已將商標申請撤回。<br />\n<br />\n對此事件白金漢宮發言人則拒絕回應，並強調，自哈利夫婦宣布將退出王室後，已多次表聲明，將不再針對此聲明發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/24/phpBvjRLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F24%2FphpBvjRLY.jpg&h=735f3c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國哈利王子與妻子梅根將在3月底，正式卸下王室職務"},{"pid":"c92586844260a507ddd22c300440c3b27a027dad","tid":1895943,"uid":77196,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:37:22.000Z","msg":"再嘈咪收返哂，睇你仲點掛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832ccfb91507df27aba2f3dd564cda767e825902","tid":1895943,"uid":282569,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"呢兩條 真係大茂利嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981077616831b493b319465a665b475cb6ea053e","tid":1895943,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:41:15.000Z","msg":"有冇註冊埋水蜜桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2d10ecbddae044e63de067a82d23a16a57c34b","tid":1895943,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:42:36.000Z","msg":"日落帝國"},{"pid":"e5702553ce1f0977ae3b3739d46abc350758fa19","tid":1895943,"uid":257622,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:45:23.000Z","msg":"又要做雞，又要攞貞節牌坊"},{"pid":"8336282e078905f6155b65fe085930ff4e66decb","tid":1895943,"uid":28068,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"唔想做野又想用個名<br />\n當人on9咩"},{"pid":"743350b015407fe0211e96a74107bb0ca7b9c60d","tid":1895943,"uid":180184,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRdiXMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRdiXMA.jpg&h=cf0204dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59a4fb5c2e50eb0066af9743731088a80a5c7264","tid":1895943,"uid":19287,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:51:33.000Z","msg":"娶著個西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be2f731f5bfde3fe0a98fb159ae67f931330fa0","tid":1895943,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"981077616831b493b319465a665b475cb6ea053e","tid":1895943,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"